name: Signpost 1
Dialogue:
NOTICE! 
 ROUTE 12 may be blocked off by a sleeping POKEMON. Detour through ROCK TUNNEL to LAVENDER TOWN. 
 VERMILION POLICE

name: Signpost 2
Dialogue:
POKEMON FAN CLUB 
 All POKEMON fans welcome!
Did you see the S.S.ANNE moored in the harbor?
We're careful about pollution! We've heard GRIMER multiplies in toxic sludge!
I'm putting up a building on this plot of land. My POKEMON is tamping the land.

name: Machop
Dialogue: Guoh! Gogogoh!
A MACHOP is stomping the land flat.

name: Center 1
Dialogue:
It is true that a higher level POKEMON will be more powerful...
But, all POKEMON will have weak points against specific types.
So, there is no universally strong POKEMON.

name: Center 2
Dialogue: My POKEMON was poisoned! It fainted while we were walking!

name: Center 3
Dialogue:
Even if they are the same level, POKEMON can have very different
abilities. A POKEMON raised by a trainer is stronger than one in
the wild.

name: Mart 1
Dialogue:
There are evil people who will use POKEMON for criminal acts.
TEAM ROCKET traffics in rare POKEMON. They also abandon POKEMON
that they consider not to be popular or useful.

name: Mart 2
Dialogue: I think POKEMON can be good or evil. It depends on the trainer.

name: Mart 3
Dialogue: I'm the FISHING GURU! I simply Looove fishing! Do you like to fish?
Oh... That's so disappointing...
Grand! I like your style! Take this and fish, young one!

name: Mart 3 after
Dialogue: Hello there, Player! How are the fish biting?
Hi! Do you have SPEAROW? Want to trade it for FARFETCH'D?
That's too bad.
...This is no SPEAROW. If you get one, trade it with me!
Okay, connect the cable like so!
Thanks pal!

name: Fan Poster 1
Dialogue: Let's all listen politely to other trainers!

name: Fan Poster 2
Dialogue: If someone brags, brag right back!

I chair the POKEMON Fan Club! I have collected over 100 POKEMON!
I'm very fussy when it comes to POKEMON! So... Did you come visit
to hear about my POKEMON?
Oh. Come back when you want to hear my story!

Good! Then listen up! My favorite RAPIDASH... It...cute...lovely...
smart...plus...amazing...you think so?...oh yes...it...stunning...
kindly...love it! Hug it...when...sleeping...warm and cuddly...
spectacular...ravishing... ...Oops! Look at the time! I kept you
too long! Thanks for hearing me out! I want you to have this!

Exchange that for a BICYCLE! Don't worry, my FEAROW will FLY me
 anywhere! So, I don't need a BICYCLE! I hope you like cycling!

name: 8 after
Dialogue: Hello, Player! Did you come see me about my POKEMON again? No? Too bad!
Our Chairman is very vocal about POKEMON.
I just love my SEEL! It squeals when I hug it!
Humph! My PIKACHU is twice as cute as that one!
I'm getting my PIDGEY to fly a letter to SAFFRON in the north!

name: Seel
Dialogue: Kyuoo!

name: Pikachu
Dialogue: Chu! Pikachu!

name: Pidgey
Dialogue: Kurukkoo!

name: Letter
Dialogue: Dear PIPPI, I hope to see you soon. I heard SAFFRON has problems with TEAM ROCKET. VERMILION appears to be safe.

name: Anne 1
Dialogue: S.S.ANNE is a famous luxury cruise ship. We visit VERMILION once a year.

name: Anne 2
Dialogue: Welcome to S.S.ANNE! Excuse me, do you have a ticket?
Sorry! You need a ticket to get aboard.
Great! Welcome to S.S.ANNE!

name: Anne 3
Dialogue: The passengers are restless! You might be challenged by the more bored ones!

name: Anne 4
Dialogue: Bonjour! I am le waiter on this ship! I will be happy to serve you anything you please! Ah! Le strong silent type!

name: Anne 5
Dialogue: You, mon petit! We're busy here! Out of the way!

name: Anne 6
Dialogue: I saw an odd ball in the trash.

name: Anne 7
Dialogue: I'm so busy I'm getting dizzy!

name: Anne 8
Dialogue: Er-hem! Indeed I am le CHEF! Le main course is
{1} Prime Beef Steak! But, have I enough fillets du beef?
{2} Eels au Barbecue! Les guests will mutiny, I fear.
{3} Salade de Salmon! Les guests may gripe it's fish again, however!

name: Anne 9
Dialogue: Snivel...Sniff... I only get to peel onions... Snivel...

name: Anne 10
Dialogue: Did you hear about SNORLAX? All it does is eat and sleep!

name: Anne 11
Dialogue: Hum-de-hum-de-ho... I peel spuds every day! Hum-hum...

name: Trainer 1
Dialogue: I travel alone on my journeys! My POKEMON are my only friends!

name: Trainer 1 after
Dialogue: You should be nice to friends!

name: Trainer 2
Dialogue: You pup! How dare you barge in!

name: Trainer 2 after
Dialogue: I wish to be left alone! Get out!
Waiter, I would like a cherry pie please!
A cruise is so elegant yet cozy!
I always travel with WIGGLYTUFF!

name: Wigglytuff
Dialogue: Puup pupuu!

name: Trainer 3
Dialogue: I collected these POKEMON from all around the world!

name: Trainer 3 after
Dialogue:
You hurt my poor worldly POKEMON! I demand that you heal them
at a POKEMON CENTER!

name: Trainer 4
Dialogue: I love POKEMON! Do you?

name: Trainer 4 after
Dialogue: Let me be your friend, OK? Then we can trade POKEMON!
We are cruising around the world.
Ssh! I'm a GLOBAL POLICE agent! I'm on the trail of TEAM ROCKET!

My buddy, MACHOKE, is super strong! He has enough STRENGTH to move
big rocks!

name: Machoke
Dialogue: Gwoh! Goggoh!

name: Trainer 5
Dialogue: My sailor's pride is at stake!

name: Trainer 5 after
Dialogue: Did you see the FISHING GURU in VERMILION CITY?

name: Trainer 6
Dialogue: You know what they say about sailors and fighting!

name: Trainer 6 after
Dialogue: Haha! Want to be a sailor, mate?

name: Trainer 7
Dialogue: I like feisty kids like you!

name: Trainer 7 after
Dialogue: Sea POKEMON live in deep water. You'll need a ROD!

name: Trainer 8
Dialogue: Us sailors have POKEMON too!

name: Trainer 8 after
Dialogue: We caught all our POKEMON while out at sea!

name: Trainer 9
Dialogue: Hello stranger! Stop and chat! All my POKEMON are from the sea!

name: Trainer 9 after
Dialogue: I was going to make you my assistant too!

name: Trainer 10
Dialogue: Matey, you're walking the plank if you lose!

name: Trainer 10 after
Dialogue: Jellyfish sometimes drift into the ship.

This ship, she is a luxury liner for trainers! At every port,
we hold parties with invited trainers!

In all my travels I've never seen any POKEMON sleep like this one!
It was something like this!

name: Trainer 11
Dialogue: Check out what I fished up!

name: Trainer 11 after
Dialogue: Party? The cruise ship's party should be over by now.

name: Trainer 12
Dialogue: Competing against the young keeps me youthful.

name: Trainer 12 after
Dialogue: 15 years ago, I would have won!
Ah yes, I have seen some POKEMON ferry people across the water!
POKEMON can CUT down small bushes.

name: Trainer 13
Dialogue: Which do you like, a strong or a rare POKEMON?

name: Trainer 13 after
Dialogue: I prefer strong and rare POKEMON.

name: Trainer 14
Dialogue: I never saw you at the party.

name: Trainer 14 after
Dialogue: Oh, I adore your strong POKEMON!

Have you gone to the SAFARI ZONE in FUCHSIA CITY? It had many rare
kinds of POKEMON!!
Me and my Daddy think the SAFARI ZONE is awesome!
The CAPTAIN looked really sick and pale!
I hear many people get seasick!
Our CAPTAIN is a sword master! He even teaches CUT to POKEMON!

name: Trainer 15
Dialogue: Ahoy there! Are you seasick?

name: Trainer 15 after
Dialogue: My Pa said there are 100 kinds of POKEMON. I think there are more.
Urf. I feel ill. I stepped out to get some air.
Scrubbing decks is hard work!

name: Trainer 16
Dialogue: Hey matey! Let's do a little jig!

name: Trainer 16 after
Dialogue: How many kinds of POKEMON do you think there are?
The party's over. The ship will be departing soon.

name: Rival_Fight
Dialogue:
Bonjour! Player! Imagine seeing you here! Player, were you really
invited? So how's your POKEDEX coming? I already caught 40 kinds,
pal! Different kinds are everywhere! Crawl around in grassy
areas!

name: Rival_Fight_after
Dialogue:
I heard there was a CUT master on board. But, he was just a
seasick, old man! But, CUT itself is really useful! 
You should go see him! Smell ya!

name: Captain
Dialogue: Ooargh... I feel hideous... Urrp! Seasick...

Player rubbed the CAPTAIN's back!
Rub-rub... Rub-rub...

Whew! Thank you! I feel much better! You want to see my CUT technique? 
 I could show you if I wasn't ill... I know! You can have this! Teach it to your POKEMOn and you can see it CUT any time!
Oh no! You have no room for this!
Whew! Now that I'm not sick any more, I guess it's time.

name: 2 after
Dialogue: The ship set sail.

name: Gym Signpost
Dialogue:
VERMILION CITY POKEMON GYM
LEADER: LT.SURGE
The Lightning American!

name: Gym Poster
Dialogue: WINNING TRAINERS: Rival

name: Gym 1
Dialogue:
Yo! Champ in making! LT.SURGE has a nickname. People refer to him
as the Lightning American! He's an expert on electric POKEMON!
Birds and water POKEMON are at risk! Beware of paralysis too!
LT.SURGE is very cautious! You'll have to break a code to get
to him!

name: Gym 1 after
Dialogue: Whew! That match was electric!

name: Trainer 1 gym
Dialogue: This is no place for kids!

name: Trainer 1 gym after
Dialogue:
LT.SURGE set up double locks! Here's a hint! When you open the 
1st lock, the 2nd lock is right next to it!

name: Trainer 2 gym
Dialogue: I'm a lightweight, but I'm good with electricity!

name: Trainer 2 gym after
Dialogue:
OK, I'll talk! LT.SURGE said he hid door switches inside 
something!

name: Trainer 3 gym
Dialogue: When I was in the Army, LT.SURGE was my strict CO!

name: Trainer 3 gym after
Dialogue: The door won't open? LT.SURGE always was cautious!

name: Lt. Surge
Dialogue:
Hey, kid! What do you think you're doing here? You won't live 
long in combat! That's for sure! I tell you kid, electric POKEMON 
saved me during the war! They zapped my enemies into paralysis! 
The same as I'll do to you!

name: Lt. Surge after
Dialogue:
A little word of advice, kid! Electricity is sure powerful! 
But, it's useless against ground-type POKEMON!
